WEBVTT

00:05.440 --> 00:08.444
(SOFT MUSIC)

00:19.200 --> 00:22.204
(INDISTINCT CHATTER)

00:30.400 --> 00:33.404
(INTENSE MUSIC)

00:35.369 --> 00:37.370
One, two...

00:37.371 --> 00:39.372
Three, four...

00:39.373 --> 00:41.374
Five, six...

00:41.375 --> 00:43.501
Seven, eight...

00:43.502 --> 00:44.719
Nine...

00:44.720 --> 00:45.754
(WIND GUSTING)

00:45.755 --> 00:47.714
Look around.

00:47.715 --> 00:51.301
There's nothing but sand
for 80 kilometers.

00:51.302 --> 00:55.930
Either you die of thirst
or you take this shortcut.

00:55.931 --> 00:57.516
Understand?

01:00.600 --> 01:03.433
(SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC)

01:10.613 --> 01:13.491
One bullet will be enough, bastard.

01:19.520 --> 01:20.601
(GASPS)

01:27.440 --> 01:29.488
(SIGHS)

01:35.721 --> 01:38.681
Lord, I know what I'm asking isn't right,

01:38.682 --> 01:41.768
but who else
can I turn to except you?

01:41.769 --> 01:44.479
Life can't be this unfair, God.

01:44.480 --> 01:46.439
My wife keeps telling me
that you punish,

01:46.440 --> 01:48.191
but not with the rod.

01:48.192 --> 01:53.530
So what kind of punishment
will those neo-Nazis receive?

01:53.531 --> 01:57.784
They beat him like an animal.

01:57.785 --> 02:02.413
Those bastards even used
a baseball bat.

02:02.414 --> 02:05.875
When I saw him at the hospital,
I barely recognized him.

02:05.876 --> 02:08.377
And the judge set them free.

02:08.378 --> 02:09.920
Free!

02:09.922 --> 02:12.090
They laughed in my face.

02:12.091 --> 02:16.177
They walked away
like nothing had happened.

02:16.178 --> 02:19.931
I know your justice is divine
and you don't make mistakes.

02:19.932 --> 02:22.892
I only want justice for my son

02:22.893 --> 02:26.729
so he can have eternal peace
with you in heaven.

02:26.730 --> 02:32.610
I ask you for justice, Lord.

02:32.611 --> 02:34.905
I leave it in your hands.

02:37.449 --> 02:38.784
Amen.

03:06.560 --> 03:09.564
(SOMBER MUSIC)

03:34.800 --> 03:36.086
(TRIGGER CLICKS)

03:40.760 --> 03:43.764
(DRAMATIC MUSIC)

03:52.316 --> 03:54.484
MAN: Here's the little bitch.
There she is.

03:54.485 --> 03:56.069
Come on! Come on!

03:56.070 --> 04:00.031
Oh, she's scared!

04:00.032 --> 04:02.700
Stop it, damn it!

04:02.701 --> 04:04.703
Where are you going, eh?

04:11.502 --> 04:13.837
Do it! Go!

04:16.130 --> 04:18.175
Stop moving, damn it!

04:23.520 --> 04:25.318
(BAT CLATTERING)

04:31.981 --> 04:33.940
How'd you get in here, asshole?

04:33.941 --> 04:35.984
Who's this monkey?

04:35.985 --> 04:38.778
You come here to get
your head bashed in,

04:38.779 --> 04:40.280
you piece of shit?

04:40.281 --> 04:42.824
I want all of you
to get on your knees

04:42.825 --> 04:44.659
and ask God for forgiveness.

04:44.660 --> 04:47.745
What's this idiot saying?

04:47.746 --> 04:49.998
Easy, bro...

04:49.999 --> 04:52.000
This fucking chimp

04:52.001 --> 04:53.627
is mine, bro!

04:57.960 --> 04:59.951
(MAN GRUNTING)

05:04.160 --> 05:07.198
(INTENSE MUSIC)

05:31.040 --> 05:32.838
(GRUNTING)

05:46.880 --> 05:50.032
(WHIMPERING)

05:51.280 --> 05:52.441
(CRACKLING)

06:06.950 --> 06:09.577
Judge not,
and you will not be judged.

06:09.578 --> 06:10.912
Condemn not,

06:10.913 --> 06:12.664
and you will not be condemned.

06:13.920 --> 06:15.240
(WHIMPERING)

06:22.200 --> 06:25.204
(SOLEMN MUSIC)

06:41.440 --> 06:44.444
(FUNKY ELECTRONIC MUSIC)

07:02.760 --> 07:04.285
WOMAN: (SINGING IN ENGLISH) ♪ You can run on ♪

08:47.080 --> 08:50.084
(OMINOUS MUSIC)

09:13.760 --> 09:15.751
(ENGINE WHIRRING)

09:17.280 --> 09:20.284
(DOGS BARKING)

09:41.160 --> 09:44.164
(DOOR CLICKS, CREAKS)

09:47.920 --> 09:49.115
(KEYS CLATTER)

10:09.320 --> 10:12.324
(MYSTERIOUS MUSIC)

10:33.383 --> 10:36.010
BOY: One... Two...

10:36.011 --> 10:39.013
Three... Four... Five...

10:39.014 --> 10:42.767
Six... Seven... Eight...

10:42.768 --> 10:45.937
Nine... Here I come!

11:04.040 --> 11:07.044
(SOMBER MUSIC)

11:08.240 --> 11:08.740
