11:27.400 --> 11:28.595
(METAL SCRAPES)

11:38.920 --> 11:40.718
(CLICKS)

11:46.665 --> 11:50.376
Do you know what the most
painful kind of torture is?

11:50.377 --> 11:52.420
What do you want
from me, Mister?

11:52.421 --> 11:55.715
Torture of the mind.

11:55.716 --> 11:59.844
For the love of God, let me go.

11:59.845 --> 12:03.597
And do you know
what the cruelest weapon is?

12:03.598 --> 12:05.558
Fear, you bastard.

12:05.559 --> 12:07.143
Why are you doing this?

12:07.144 --> 12:09.603
Are you in fear for your life?

12:09.604 --> 12:12.858
There are plenty of things
worse than death.

12:15.110 --> 12:18.738
Who do you think suffered more?

12:18.739 --> 12:20.906
Your son?

12:20.907 --> 12:25.202
Or you when you saw
how he ended up?

12:25.203 --> 12:26.620
The neo-Nazis...

12:26.621 --> 12:28.831
The neo-Nazis sent you.

12:28.832 --> 12:30.958
I don't have anything
to do with them.

12:30.959 --> 12:33.085
I don't know you, Mister.

12:33.086 --> 12:35.713
You're not afraid
of death, are you?

12:35.714 --> 12:38.382
You're a man of faith.

12:38.383 --> 12:40.760
If you die, you'll be reunited

12:40.761 --> 12:42.970
with your son in heaven.

12:42.971 --> 12:45.765
That's what you want, right?

12:45.766 --> 12:49.602
Now, listen to me
very carefully.

12:49.603 --> 12:51.396
I want you to choose.

12:52.689 --> 12:55.608
Either you burn
until you die...

12:55.609 --> 12:57.109
Or you can avoid the pain

12:57.110 --> 12:59.070
and pull the trigger.

13:02.073 --> 13:04.450
Easy, bastard.

13:04.451 --> 13:05.911
Easy.

13:10.791 --> 13:12.583
I know what you're thinking.

13:12.584 --> 13:16.045
Suicide is a sin
in your religion.

13:16.046 --> 13:19.215
But your God will understand.

13:19.216 --> 13:21.675
You were forced to do it.

13:21.676 --> 13:26.180
I am freeing you.

13:26.181 --> 13:29.391
Because I'm tracking his blood.

13:29.392 --> 13:31.227
If he helped you,

13:31.228 --> 13:33.146
then you must die.

13:35.320 --> 13:36.481
(FLICKS LIGHTER)

13:36.483 --> 13:39.318
No. No.

13:39.319 --> 13:41.279
No! No! No!

13:50.000 --> 13:51.229
(GUNSHOT)

13:56.600 --> 13:59.604
(SEAGULLS SCREECHING)

14:09.400 --> 14:12.404
(MELANCHOLY MUSIC)

14:34.040 --> 14:37.044
(FOREBODING MUSIC)

14:44.301 --> 14:46.553
"See You Next Summer"

15:19.680 --> 15:20.966
(DOOR CREAKS)

15:26.360 --> 15:29.364
(BIRD CHIRPING)

15:40.960 --> 15:41.959
(CHUCKLES) 1.

15:41.960 --> 15:43.678
It's great. It really is.

15:56.200 --> 15:58.430
The coast is easy in.
It's easy out.

16:10.400 --> 16:11.720
It's-

16:13.515 --> 16:15.642
(IN SPANISH) One moment.

16:15.720 --> 16:17.370
Yeah. Listen. I got to go.

16:24.526 --> 16:26.027
Good morning, sir.

16:27.240 --> 16:28.988
So where's my money?

16:28.989 --> 16:31.907
Where's the money,
you dumb shit?

16:31.908 --> 16:33.446
I'm working on it, sir.

16:33.447 --> 16:35.033
He's working on it, sir.

16:36.200 --> 16:37.319
(STAMMERING)

16:37.320 --> 16:38.481
Can he work harder?

16:43.336 --> 16:46.255
He says that Americans
are practical.

16:46.256 --> 16:48.298
If you cannot do the job,
then he is going to kill you.

16:48.299 --> 16:50.050
Mr. Bradock.

16:50.051 --> 16:51.635
I just wanted you to know

16:51.636 --> 16:54.888
we may not have the money
in time for the deal.

16:54.889 --> 16:56.057
Oh.

17:06.319 --> 17:07.481
I had some money,

17:10.571 --> 17:13.031
He says that the only thing

17:13.032 --> 17:15.034
you are good at is jerking off,

17:15.035 --> 17:17.661
and he does not know how
he ended up hiring you.

17:17.662 --> 17:18.954
Tell him I think
I know who has it,

17:18.954 --> 17:20.957
and that we are pressing him.

17:21.160 --> 17:23.766
He says that he
has been "squeezing."

17:25.599 --> 17:26.954
He's been squeezing?

17:30.200 --> 17:31.429
It's beautiful.

17:37.682 --> 17:39.224
He is asking if you

17:39.225 --> 17:42.436
are a poet now,
you stupid fuck?

17:42.437 --> 17:43.896
If you didn't bring
what he asked for,

17:43.897 --> 17:45.398
then what the hell
are you doing here?

17:47.120 --> 17:49.794
